  "content": "<p data-pid=\"CJL-ehvh\">写写自己的入坑过程吧：</p><p data-pid=\"HGGvX4N3\">citrus入坑，但是现在回味起来，是一锅玻璃渣糖浆，劲很大。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-936a43dabaedc36259dbb6789ad0fdaa_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"480\" data-original-token=\"v2-936a43dabaedc36259dbb6789ad0fdaa\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-010c4ba55eec9e2a56872e80965819ec_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"360\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;360&#39; height=&#39;480&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"480\" data-original-token=\"v2-936a43dabaedc36259dbb6789ad0fdaa\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-010c4ba55eec9e2a56872e80965819ec_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"360\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-936a43dabaedc36259dbb6789ad0fdaa_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"WeRTNUG2\">遇到《终将》，甜味细腻的——胃药，品得越细，越能感受那种纠结。</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a4acca90d93a906c6def7ea932985dc0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1324\" data-original-token=\"v2-a4acca90d93a906c6def7ea932985dc0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e7d5f052460d800ea7fb8d8a326eed9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a4acca90d93a906c6def7ea932985dc0_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;1324&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1324\" data-original-token=\"v2-a4acca90d93a906c6def7ea932985dc0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e7d5f052460d800ea7fb8d8a326eed9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a4acca90d93a906c6def7ea932985dc0_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a4acca90d93a906c6def7ea932985dc0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"j2SYV74k\">《利兹与青鸟》，纯粹、空灵以及（非受众可能会睡着），尝起来像是很高级的吐司？得多嚼一会儿才能体会到甜味的本质。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b391d4ade23619f25811953b643c3107_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"382\" data-original-token=\"v2-b391d4ade23619f25811953b643c3107\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ced6f2747428b2932a4bc2b0e9f53baf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"270\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;270&#39; height=&#39;382&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"382\" data-original-token=\"v2-b391d4ade23619f25811953b643c3107\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ced6f2747428b2932a4bc2b0e9f53baf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"270\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b391d4ade23619f25811953b643c3107_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"zu-57S2t\">以上是我看过的番，同时也补了漫画，然后就入坑了。</p><p data-pid=\"6cfjWMPF\">开始找漫画来看</p><p data-pid=\"CGGPRTkA\">《加濑同学》，巧克力蘸蜂蜜，甜得心都化了。加濑痴汉！（划掉</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2a0c5f22339d5dee0117f58e7d47955_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-original-token=\"v2-a2a0c5f22339d5dee0117f58e7d47955\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d8d021b80e524f4a878cf355fa58a57_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"270\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;270&#39; height=&#39;360&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-original-token=\"v2-a2a0c5f22339d5dee0117f58e7d47955\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d8d021b80e524f4a878cf355fa58a57_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"270\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2a0c5f22339d5dee0117f58e7d47955_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"HVj9DUqC\">《恋语轻唱》，这个发色跟终将撞了吧。。。出的话数不多，暂不讲感觉。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2f1d6a0c7ba18e860e25982ab7cdfed_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-original-token=\"v2-a2f1d6a0c7ba18e860e25982ab7cdfed\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4e2300c4cff75a7e28030321632c59fa_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"270\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;270&#39; height=&#39;360&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-original-token=\"v2-a2f1d6a0c7ba18e860e25982ab7cdfed\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4e2300c4cff75a7e28030321632c59fa_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"270\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2f1d6a0c7ba18e860e25982ab7cdfed_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"d6kJwIOW\">然后又开始在轻小说里面找，结果遇到了入间人间：</p><p data-pid=\"0bP7YZtw\">《安达与岛村》，不良少女变忠犬，慢热，前期看得真滴急，感觉是酒心巧克力，入间老师写的少女心看多了真的会醉哦。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-51e126219e425fe1a20daf0c7faa44a3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"364\" data-original-token=\"v2-51e126219e425fe1a20daf0c7faa44a3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-90e733ab1f05304474ac0d8987b62e73_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-51e126219e425fe1a20daf0c7faa44a3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;500&#39; height=&#39;364&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"364\" data-original-token=\"v2-51e126219e425fe1a20daf0c7faa44a3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-90e733ab1f05304474ac0d8987b62e73_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-51e126219e425fe1a20daf0c7faa44a3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-51e126219e425fe1a20daf0c7faa44a3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Yr96kMSO\">《少女妄想中》，短篇集，十分电波，感觉自己吃的是外星糖果。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa180fab77b19c3a2652dc9e542301d2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"387\" data-original-token=\"v2-fa180fab77b19c3a2652dc9e542301d2\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f53d26b31b2f606f6cb231ac5f219183_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"270\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;270&#39; height=&#39;387&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"387\" data-original-token=\"v2-fa180fab77b19c3a2652dc9e542301d2\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f53d26b31b2f606f6cb231ac5f219183_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"270\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa180fab77b19c3a2652dc9e542301d2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"nQ0v2Pgq\">《佐伯沙弥香的追忆》，佐伯女士届到了，不过还没看。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b24ae45501af3177511fec465eedb876_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"383\" data-original-token=\"v2-b24ae45501af3177511fec465eedb876\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-01e8b3f8d28a4d3cd396f8ded0e3fa9d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"270\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;270&#39; height=&#39;383&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"270\" data-rawheight=\"383\" data-original-token=\"v2-b24ae45501af3177511fec465eedb876\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-01e8b3f8d28a4d3cd396f8ded0e3fa9d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"270\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b24ae45501af3177511fec465eedb876_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"V-h79S_0\">最后进化成了百合脑，甚至在 Gal 里面找起百合来：</p><p data-pid=\"XqJAh_RQ\">（以下两部都是国gal）</p><p data-pid=\"ZaHHLhtg\">《寄甡 Symbiotic Love》，这就是在刀尖上舔糖了，刀就在那儿，舔或不舔，这是个问题。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a8039f15e404859043a379a2a0e6bcd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1234\" data-rawheight=\"617\" data-original-token=\"v2-2a8039f15e404859043a379a2a0e6bcd\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9649a9b1be51c5ee5b010bc12ad5aa58_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1234\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2a8039f15e404859043a379a2a0e6bcd_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1234&#39; height=&#39;617&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1234\" data-rawheight=\"617\" data-original-token=\"v2-2a8039f15e404859043a379a2a0e6bcd\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9649a9b1be51c5ee5b010bc12ad5aa58_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1234\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2a8039f15e404859043a379a2a0e6bcd_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a8039f15e404859043a379a2a0e6bcd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Nu_WYa0j\">《千面 Melancholy Love》，“优等生”X“不良少女”，夜来香、勿忘我、千层雪，打通了BE才能体会到HE的不易。有一种喝着加了糖的黑咖啡，糖化得不是很均匀的感觉。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-49167662eacf61bf8d6c60e976f54d97_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"997\" data-rawheight=\"715\" data-original-token=\"v2-49167662eacf61bf8d6c60e976f54d97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f7d801d6f664ee8481c352dcbae6d48_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"997\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-49167662eacf61bf8d6c60e976f54d97_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;997&#39; height=&#39;715&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"997\" data-rawheight=\"715\" data-original-token=\"v2-49167662eacf61bf8d6c60e976f54d97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f7d801d6f664ee8481c352dcbae6d48_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"997\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-49167662eacf61bf8d6c60e976f54d97_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-49167662eacf61bf8d6c60e976f54d97_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"nLomPG0H\">以上就是我能想起来的看过的百合作品了，目前还有几个想看还没开始看的作品，比如很有名的 flowers 系列。</p>",
